---
layout: base.njk
title: LaikaCMS Eleventy starter — Home
---
<p>
  Edit posts at <a href="http://localhost:3001/admin">the admin server</a> (Decap CMS).
  Content is stored on disk under <code>content/posts/</code>; Eleventy regenerates
  this site whenever a file changes.
</p>
<ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
{% for post in collections.posts %}
  <li style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
    <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title or post.fileSlug }}</a>
    {% if post.data.date %}
      <small style="margin-left: 0.5rem; color: #666;">{{ post.data.date.toLocaleDateString() }}</small>
    {% endif %}
  </li>
{% endfor %}
{% if not collections.posts.length %}
  <li><em>No posts yet — add one in the admin UI.</em></li>
{% endif %}
</ul>
